Act of WAR - DVD9 ---> DVD5 INSTRUCTIONS
First grab i6comp from here: myplc.com/sony/bin/i6comp.zip

THIS IS FOR ENGLISH ONLY!!! replace with language of your choice:

16comp l data2.cab will list then event ID filename... make note of the language you want to keep..

Then extract the ISO to your HD NTFS needed as over 5G

Goto video folder and delete all the wav files EXCEPT ENG_Cutscene_00.wav 

DELETE Directx folder

DELETE Language (readme.txt) files from Root

Unzip 16comp to root dir

goto command prompt root dir of your extracted iso

16comp d data2.cab 90 datav_fr.dat

16comp d data2.cab 91 datas_fr.dat

16comp d data2.cab 92 datav_de.dat

16comp d data2.cab 93 datas_de.dat

16comp d data2.cab 94 datav_it.dat

16comp d data2.cab 95 datas_it.dat

16comp d data2.cab 96 datav_es.dat

16comp d data2.cab 97 datav_es.dat

You NOW have a filesize of ~3.1G which you CAN burn to NORMAL DVD

The label to use is AOW
